<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.5">
<l>vāyeṭutta mantirattā lantaṇartañ ceytoḻilkaḷ</l>
<l>tīyeṭuttu maṟaivaḷarkkun tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>tāyeṭutta ciṟukōluk kuḷaintōṭit tayiruṇṭa</l>
<l>vāytuṭaitta maintaṉukki ḻantēṉeṉ varivaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my striped bangles to the boy who ate the curds,</l>
<l>And running, suffering from the little rod his mother held, wiped his mouth,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram where priests propagate the Vedas,</l>
<l>Upholding the fires and their required duties</l>
<l rend="indent">with mantras sung from [their] lips.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
